==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Habenaria
<hw>Habenaria</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>A genus of chiefly
terrestrial orchids with tubers or fleshy roots often having long
slender spurs and petals and lip lobes; it includes species formerly
placed in the genus <gen>Gymnadeniopsis</gen>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> genus <gen>Habenaria</gen>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

